        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
                Contact Us
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-xl text-primary-100">
                Connect with LibraryX. We're here to answer your questions and provide assistance with our services.
            </p>
